      i0.ɵɵelementStart(158, "div", 67)(159, "p", 68);
      i0.ɵɵtext(160, " We're thrilled to have you join us as we begin our forever journey! Here's everything you need to know to make the day magical for everyone. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(161, "p", 69)(162, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(163, "\uD83D\uDC83 Let's Celebrate!");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(164, " We want you to have the time of your life at our wedding! While the dance floor is open for your best moves, we kindly ask everyone to respect our simple house rules to ensure everyone has an amazing experience. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(165, "p", 69)(166, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(167, "\uD83D\uDCF8 Capture the Moments");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(168, " - While we have professional photographers, we'd love to see the day through your eyes too! Feel free to take plenty of pictures and share them on your social media pages using our hashtags #everydayisdayone and #loveInVAir25. Please upload your favorite shots to our ");
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(169, "a", 71);
      i0.ɵɵtext(170, "shared Google Drive folder");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(171, " so we can include them in our memories. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(172, "span", 72);
      i0.ɵɵtext(173, "Important: Please only add your photos and never delete any files that others have uploaded. Each photo is a precious memory for us!");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(174, "span", 73);
      i0.ɵɵtext(175, "\uD83D\uDCF1 ");
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(176, "span", 74);
      i0.ɵɵtext(177, "For iPhone users:");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(178, " Kindly ensure you have the Google Drive app downloaded from the ");
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(179, "a", 75);
      i0.ɵɵtext(180, "App Store");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(181, " and sign in to enable you to upload pictures to the shared folder.");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(182, " We'll create a beautiful digital album with all these special moments. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(183, "p", 69)(184, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(185, "\uD83D\uDCBA Seating Arrangements");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(186, " - We've carefully planned our seating to ensure everyone's comfort and enjoyment. We kindly ask that you sit at the tables reserved for you as directed by our ushers. This helps us maintain the organization of the event and ensures you're seated with people you'll enjoy celebrating with. Our thoughtful ushers will be happy to assist you in finding your designated seats. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(187, "p", 69)(188, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(189, "\uD83D\uDE4F Church Etiquette");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(190, " - The ceremony is a special moment we've been dreaming about. Please arrive 30 minutes early to be seated, silence your phones, and maintain a respectful atmosphere during this sacred time. Children are welcome, but if they become restless, we have a designated quiet area. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(191, "p", 69)(192, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(193, "\uD83C\uDFE8 Accommodation");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(194, " - For the best experience and easy transportation to all events, we've arranged special rates at Jos Business School and Villa Grande Hotels. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(195, "p", 69)(196, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(197, "\uD83D\uDCF1 Need Help?");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(198, " Our amazing coordination team is here for you! Rather than approaching the bride and groom with questions or concerns, please contact our wedding coordinators at the numbers below. They're equipped to handle everything from emergency situations to helping you find the restrooms. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(199, "p", 69)(200, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(201, "\uD83D\uDCB8 Gift of Cash");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(202, " - For those who wish to shower us with cash gifts during the celebration, we appreciate your generosity! Please handle the naira notes with care and respect. Our ushers will provide elegant envelopes if you prefer to give your gift that way. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵelementStart(203, "p", 69)(204, "span", 70);
      i0.ɵɵtext(205, "\uD83D\uDE97 Transportation");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
      i0.ɵɵtext(206, " - Please note that transportation to and from venues is not provided by the couple. Bolt rides are readily available and operate efficiently throughout all our event locations - we recommend using this service. For those driving, we kindly encourage you to offer rides to other guests when possible. Rest assured that secure parking is available at all venues for your convenience. ");
      i0.ɵɵelementEnd();
