                  </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">💃 Let's Celebrate!</span> We want you to have the time of your life at our wedding! While the dance floor is open for your best moves, we kindly ask everyone to respect our simple house rules to ensure everyone has an amazing experience.
                  </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">📸 Capture the Moments</span> - While we have professional photographers, we'd love to see the day through your eyes too! Feel free to take plenty of pictures and share them on your social media pages using our hashtags #everydayisdayone and #loveInVAir25. Please upload your favorite shots to our <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1XIvJSSvzQGbTroXYUflOVuz8loIIQS6s?usp=sharing" class="text-[#7851A9] font-semibold underline hover:text-[#B695C0]" target="_blank">shared Google Drive folder</a> so we can include them in our memories. <span class="italic font-medium">Important: Please only add your photos and never delete any files that others have uploaded. Each photo is a precious memory for us!</span> 

                    <span class="block mt-2">📱 <span class="font-medium">For iPhone users:</span> Kindly ensure you have the Google Drive app downloaded from the <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/google-drive/id507874739" class="text-[#7851A9] font-semibold underline hover:text-[#B695C0]" target="_blank">App Store</a> and sign in to enable you to upload pictures to the shared folder.</span>

                    We'll create a beautiful digital album with all these special moments.
                   </p>

                   <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">💺 Seating Arrangements</span> - We've carefully planned our seating to ensure everyone's comfort and enjoyment. We kindly ask that you sit at the tables reserved for you as directed by our ushers. This helps us maintain the organization of the event and ensures you're seated with people you'll enjoy celebrating with. Our thoughtful ushers will be happy to assist you in finding your designated seats.
                   </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">🙏 Church Etiquette</span> - The ceremony is a special moment we've been dreaming about. Please arrive 30 minutes early to be seated, silence your phones, and maintain a respectful atmosphere during this sacred time. Children are welcome, but if they become restless, we have a designated quiet area.
                  </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">🏨 Accommodation</span> - For the best experience and easy transportation to all events, we've arranged special rates at Jos Business School and Villa Grande Hotels. 
                  </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">📱 Need Help?</span> Our amazing coordination team is here for you! Rather than approaching the bride and groom with questions or concerns, please contact our wedding coordinators at the numbers below. They're equipped to handle everything from emergency situations to helping you find the restrooms.
                  </p>


                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">💸 Gift of Cash</span> - For those who wish to shower us with cash gifts during the celebration, we appreciate your generosity! Please handle the naira notes with care and respect. Our ushers will provide elegant envelopes if you prefer to give your gift that way.
                  </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">🚗 Transportation</span> - Please note that transportation to and from venues is not provided by the couple. Bolt rides are readily available and operate efficiently throughout all our event locations - we recommend using this service. For those driving, we kindly encourage you to offer rides to other guests when possible. Rest assured that secure parking is available at all venues for your convenience.
                   </p>

                  <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#7851A9]">⏰ Timeline</span> - We value your time and have planned a seamless flow of events. The ceremony begins precisely at 10am, followed by photos, with the reception starting immediatly after at the designated venue. 
